@startuml
title 15 - Fluxo Alternativo - Falha na Criação do Shipment e Compensações

autonumber
queue "Kafka" as Kafka
participant "Order Service" as Order
participant "Shipment Service" as Shipment
participant "Carrier Service" as Carrier
participant "Inventory Service" as Inventory
participant "Fulfillment Center Service" as FC
participant "Payment Platform" as Payment
participant "Notification Service" as Notification

database "Order DB" as OrderDb

Kafka -> Order: Reservas e autorização concluídas
activate Order
Order -> Kafka: CreateShipmentCommand
deactivate Order

Kafka -> Shipment: CreateShipmentCommand
activate Shipment
Shipment -> Shipment: Aplica inbox/idempotência
Shipment -> Shipment: Cria shipment PendingCarrierBooking
Shipment -> Carrier: Booking de shipment

alt Erro permanente no Carrier
  Carrier --> Shipment: 422 / regra logística rejeitada
  Shipment -> Shipment: Marca shipment Failed
  Shipment -> Kafka: ShipmentCreationFailedIntegrationEvent
else Tentativas esgotadas
  Carrier --> Shipment: Erros transitórios repetidos
  Shipment -> Shipment: Agenda retries com backoff
  Shipment -> Shipment: Excede limite de tentativas
  Shipment -> Kafka: ShipmentCreationFailedIntegrationEvent
end
deactivate Shipment

Kafka -> Order: ShipmentCreationFailedIntegrationEvent
activate Order
Order -> OrderDb: Cancela pedido antes da etapa final
Order -> Kafka: ReleaseInventoryReservationCommand
Order -> Kafka: ReleaseFulfillmentCapacityCommand
Order -> Kafka: VoidPaymentAuthorizationCommand
Order -> Kafka: OrderCancelledIntegrationEvent
deactivate Order

Kafka -> Inventory: ReleaseInventoryReservationCommand
Kafka -> FC: ReleaseFulfillmentCapacityCommand
Kafka -> Payment: VoidPaymentAuthorizationCommand
Kafka -> Notification: OrderCancelledIntegrationEvent
Notification -> Notification: Notifica cancelamento por falha logística

@enduml
